				<p>Kelly and others with chilling questions: If you have any hope of the crackers retaining their shape, the chilling process is essential. Which reminds me, I need to add a note that I actually did it for half the time in the freezer (once rolled out). They can&#8217;t be too firmed up before you put them in the oven.</p>
