				<p>Made the graham crackers over the weekend and found that they burned at 350 degrees, even in the 15 minute window.  The last batch was baked at 325 degrees and turned out perfect.  Might have been my oven but I thought I&#8217;d toss that out.</p>
	</li>
		
		
		
	
<li class="commentbody" id="comment-473202">
