				<p>Made these for a pumpkin cream pie crust for Thanksgiving and they ARE INCREDIBLE.</p>
<p>They TOTALLY outshone the pie&#8230;but that is a good problem to have! I froze the rest and will take them out for another pie at Christmas. I&#8217;ll look for a more robustly-flavored filling next time. Maybe something cranberry? Ideas?</p>
<p>Thanks so MUCH!!!!!!!!!</p>
	</li>
		
		
		
	
